{"tid":1894041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有朋友還押而又需要口罩嘅同我入嚟","createTime":"2020-02-23T16:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T19:14:56.000Z","uid":81424,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"72fd3e83a96c5cb523ce6573595d3d4238cb2b80","tid":1894041,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T16:12:11.000Z","msg":"【義贈口罩予還柙或在囚義士】<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有朋友為反逃犯修例的還柙或在囚義士，我們會預留每位囚友最多20個口罩，或按需要量。<br />\n請聯絡 #國民支援 （尋求支援：9030 2853（鄭錦滿））登記及領取，或直接委托我們送遞。<br />\n<br />\n在此，再次感謝支持者的心意及信任，好人一生平安。<br />\n<br />\n備註：我們會核對基本資料，每個在囚編號限取一次，敬希體諒。<br />\n<br />\n「國民支援配對計劃」背景：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/111284017035418/posts/123171325846687/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F111284017035418%2Fposts%2F123171325846687%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=e3b4312c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/111284017035418/posts/123171325846687/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n「#國民支援」目的是建立一個人道支援網絡，包括：<br />\n一、尋求支援（法律、生活、醫療等）：9030-2853（鄭錦滿）；<br />\n二、提供支援（工作、實習、捐款等）：5596-8181（Kina）。<br />\n<br />\n#Telegram：@blesshongkongmatchingscheme<br />\n#國泰民安人道支援 Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/blesshkmatchingscheme\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fblesshkmatchingscheme&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=ff98dd55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/blesshkmatchingscheme</a><br />\n<br />\n#國民支援<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p720x720/87151684_139190557578097_4682146666315251712_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_sid=a61e81&amp;_nc_ohc=KDA5bKek-ncAX8D5Uur&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=f75d91ee91c72c2dbb7f540f2a47f653&amp;oe=5EF84F77\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp720x720%2F87151684_139190557578097_46821466663152517